#

Buffalo Chicken Wrap

20 min
$8
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickWrapSpicy

Description

A zesty and satisfying wrap filled with spicy buffalo chicken and fresh veggies.

Ingredients

  • cooked chicken breast: 1 cup, shredded
  • buffalo sauce: 1/2 cup
  • tortilla wraps: 2 large
  • ranch dressing: 2 tablespoons
  • lettuce: 1 cup, shredded
  • tomato: 1, diced
  • cheddar cheese: 1/2 cup, shredded
